manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.cwi.MainActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.title: Crypto Wallet Integrator
playstore_details.description:
Crypto Wallet Integrator (CWI) gives you possibility to see total balance of each cryptocurrency wallet you have in one place no matter of its type: crypto exchange balance, hardware wallet, mobile or desktop wallet and even paper wallet.

No need to open all crypto wallets each time you want to see their total balances, just collect wallets in one place using our crypto aggregator and easily check totals.

In CWI you can aggregate wallets and see:
- balance of each crypto wallet you have -> coins and fiat equivalent
- balance of crypto asset (e.g. total BTC of all Bitcoin wallets) -> coins and fiat equivalent
- total balance of all wallets and digital assets in fiat equivalent

All fiat equivalents calculated dynamically according to current exchange rates on the crypto market. You will always know how much traditional money you have at the moment.

Crypto Wallet Integrator completely secure - all your blockchain wallets and crypto balances are stored ONLY on your mobile phone.

To start using application you just need to add your wallets. This can be done in two ways:
1. Wallet public address - balance will be updated automatically based on info from blockchain network;
2. Wallet amount - feel even more safe, but with one downside, you need to update balance manually each time you pay/receive cryptocurrency

SECURITY
We will NEVER ask you for private keys of your crypto wallet.
We suggest you NEVER share/copy/paste private keys.
We NEVER store your public addresses or balances outside of your mobile phone.

SUPPORTED COINS:
- Bitcoin (BTC)
- Ethereum (ETH)
- Ripple (XRP)

ABOUT CWI
Created by crypto enthusiasts for other crypto enthusiasts :)
If you see some things that can be improved or have any other questions - please contact us: crypto.wallets.integrator@gmail.com
